    # ermy_game "I don’t think I’m supposed to be here."
    ermy_game "しかし、ここにも俺の居場所がなかった。"

# game/room.rpy:547
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_7df35926:

    # ermy_game "I spent enough time in this otherwise unremarkable room, spare for a very weird note on a whiteboard."
    ermy_game "この暗い部屋にどれぐらいいるのかわからない。この白板以外何もない部屋に。"

# game/room.rpy:548
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_a42734e2:

    # ermy_game "To leave this room, you must tell me the answer."
    ermy_game "白板に\"部屋を出たければ、質問に答えなさい\"と書いてある。"

# game/room.rpy:549
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_2d473ecc:

    # ermy_game "What does it mean? Who 'me'? What’s the question to begin with?"
    ermy_game "どういう意味？誰に答えないといけない？そもそもどの質問に答えないといけない？"

# game/room.rpy:550
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_993cdf82:

    # ermy_game "The only semblance of a hint came from a few more words below. Four in total: \"Love\", \"Hate\", \"Life\", \"Death\"."
    ermy_game "他に白板に\"愛\", \"憎しみ\", \"生\", \"死\"という言葉が書かれてある。"

# game/room.rpy:551
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_7594ef6b:

    # ermy_game "Well… so what of it?"
    ermy_game "どうしよう？"

# game/room.rpy:552
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/room.rpy:559
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_ff49ed50:

    # e1 "All this makes no sense"
    e1 "意味わからない。"

# game/room.rpy:561
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_c345e091:

    # s1 "I know, dear. What is the question, I wonder? That’s what my friend and I are trying to realize."
    s1 "私も。何の質問なんだろう？友達と一緒にずっと頭を痛める。"

# game/room.rpy:563
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_383636ae:

    # ee "A young woman appears seemingly out of nowhere. Dressed in an overly tight nurse uniform, she carries a syringe filled with a strange, bright liquid."
    ee "急に若い女性が現れてきた。看護婦のタイトな白衣を着て、輝いている液体の注射器を持っている。"

# game/room.rpy:564
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_cb8159dd:

    # e1 "Who are you?"
    e1 "あなた、誰？"

# game/room.rpy:566
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_dcafaa9b:

    # s1 "My name is Sophie. Nice to meet you! As for my friend, he doesn’t talk much, so I’m afraid I can’t introduce him to you properly."
    s1 "ソフィーという。初めまして！友達はあまりしゃべらないから紹介できない。"

# game/room.rpy:568
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_aa0ed32b:

    # e1 "Your friend?"
    e1 "友達？"

# game/room.rpy:570
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_c8ec2342:

    # s1 "Yes, here, right in my hand. My precious friend who always knows the truth. Always but today it seems."
    s1 "手に持っている友達よ。なんでも知っている大切な友達。でも、今日に限って答えがわかってないようだ。"

# game/room.rpy:572
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_df2dc478:

    # ee "I thought back to my military training… The best way to deal with mentally unstable people is to take them seriously."
    ee "軍隊でわかったのは、精神障害の人と真剣に話したほうがいい。"

# game/room.rpy:573
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_d0f3046b:

    # e1 "I guess it’s nice to have such a wise friend."
    e1 "賢い友達がいると頼もしいね。"

# game/room.rpy:575
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_09b3c39d:

    # s1 "More like \"persistent\", I should say. It takes my friend quite some time to kick in but then there’s no stopping him, and you’re guaranteed to tell me everything I want."
    s1 "賢いというより\"しつこい\"かな。時間をもとめるが、結局友達のおかげで私が知りたいことをあなたが全部話してくれるの。"

# game/room.rpy:579
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_6293d535:

    # ee "She moves closer, and I can’t help but notice that the button on Sophie’s blouse is about to be ripped off by her… well…"
    ee "近づいてくると、白衣のボタンがとれそうだと気づいてしまう。"

# game/room.rpy:584
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_b5889205:

    # s1 "Hey darling, care to have a taste? Who knows, maybe you’re just pretending, not willing to tell me the answer… Hey, I really want to get out of this place. I don’t think I’m supposed be here."
    s1 "ダーリン、試してみる？ただ答えがわからないふりをしてるだろう？…　ここを出たい。私はここにいるべきではないと思う。"

# game/room.rpy:592
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_e99bbab8:

    # m1 "Stay away, she’s clearly out of her mind."
    m1 "近づくな！あの人が狂ってる。"

# game/room.rpy:594
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_9f1f1f9d:

    # ee "This room gets more crowded, now that a second girl, wrapped up in a latex costume serving presumably no other purpose rather than an aesthetic one, shows up in front of me."
    ee "部屋にラテックスを着ているもう一人の女性が現れてきた。"

# game/room.rpy:596
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_f43514bc:

    # s1 "I’m much saner than you… Megan, right? At least I’m not making up a ridiculous explanation of what bound us all together here like you do."
    s1 "私はあなたより正気だ…　メガンだっけ？ここにいる私たちの絆などばかばかしいこと言わないし。"

# game/room.rpy:600
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_c8a8866f:

    # m1 "It’s not ridiculous, it’s true. I come from an era far more advanced than yours, I know things you can’t even imagine."
    m1 "これは現実だ。あなたよりはるかに進んだ時代からきて、あなたが想像もできないことを知っている。"

# game/room.rpy:604
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_58bc8214:

    # s1 "See? That’s what I’m talking about. Megan think she’s from the future."
    s1 "だろう？メガンは自分が未来から来たって思ってる。"

# game/room.rpy:608
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_a148509d:

    # m1 "Still don’t believe me? Fine. What’s your last memory before you got here? I’m asking you as well, by the way. What’s your name?"
    m1 "まだ信じてくれないの？ここに来る前最後の思い出は何？あなたも答えて。名前は？"

# game/room.rpy:610
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_74f4a0d0:

    # e1 "Hermes."
    e1 "ヘルメース。"

# game/room.rpy:612
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_54bce0ef:

    # m1 "So, Hermes, do you remember anything?"
    m1 "じゃ、ヘルメース。何か覚えてる？"

# game/room.rpy:615
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_6652deee:

    # e1 "I heard the phone ringing somewhere very close to where I was."
    e1 "どこか近くに電話がなる音が聞こえた。"

# game/room.rpy:617
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_49075dd6:

    # ee "The second I say that the phone starts ringing again. Ring-ring… ring-ring… like those machines in old detective phones."
    ee "そう言ったらまた電話の音が響く。探偵小説にあるような古い電話の音が。ジャンジャン…　ジャンジャン…"

# game/room.rpy:619
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_6932f0a0:

    # ee "The sound becomes more and more loud. My head hurts! Someone should stop it. Pick up the phone, please…"
    ee "音がだんだん大きくなる。頭痛い！誰か止めてくれ。電話に出てくれ…"

# game/room.rpy:621
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_24caa050:

    # m1 "What did you say?"
    m1 "今何言った？"

# game/room.rpy:623
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_36b25b49:

    # e1 "Can you hear it?"
    e1 "聞こえる？"

# game/room.rpy:625
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_ea6891f3:

    # m1 "Hear what?"
    m1 "何を？"

# game/room.rpy:627
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_43daaf35:

    # e1 "That phone ringing over and over again… Jeez, it really gets on my nerves."
    e1 "あの電話がなっている音を…　あぁ、もう耐えられない。"

# game/room.rpy:629
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_abd216de:

    # m1 "My, this room must be a hangout spot for weirdos. And I thought it couldn’t be worse than when our spaceship was invaded by those creatures…"
    m1 "なるほど、私、狂った人たちと一緒に部屋に絞められたか。宇宙船にあの異星人に侵入されたときより大変なことが起こるわけないと思っていたのに…"

# game/room.rpy:632
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_adf1fed7:

    # s1 "Please don’t mention this word again, Megan."
    s1 "もうその言葉を言わないで、メガン。"

# game/room.rpy:636
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_80ad3d76:

    # m1 "What are you talking about?"
    m1 "何の言葉？"

# game/room.rpy:640
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_c226c8fb:

    # s1 "Hang, you said… what a painful word. I was doing my daily routine, helping people to open up and talk… the guy we had back then, he just couldn’t relax, he was so nervous!"
    s1 "絞められたって。心苦しい言葉だ…　普通に仕事をして、話したくない人を話せるように頑張ってて。でも、あの人が緊張してリラックスできなかったようで、なかなかしゃべらなくて。"

# game/room.rpy:641
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_a9f9cb3e:

    # s1 "\"You won’t get a single word out of me!\" he shouted, rolling eyes like a madman. So silly of him! Then I heard the footsteps…"
    s1 "\"一言も言わせない！\"って叫んでてさ、狂人のようにきょろきょろして、あのあほが！そのあと、足音が聞こえて…"

# game/room.rpy:642
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_14c1ee5f:

    # s1 "Bam! They ran out the door and barged in. \"Hey girl, nothing personal, but we don’t like to see our friend suffer. That’s a nice rope you tied him with, by the way. Why don’t we really put it to use?\""
    s1 "ドン！部屋に走り込んで。\"あのね、ごめんけど、友達が苦しんでいるのを見たくない。いいロープで縛ったね、そのロープ使おうかな\"って。"

# game/room.rpy:644
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_8242434b:

    # ee "Sophie shivers and stops talking."
    ee "ソフィーが震えてきて、話を辞める。"

# game/room.rpy:646
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_b319f4e8:

    # m1 "Hm… I think I just realized that, although we came from different eras, we share one thing in common."
    m1 "んじゃ…　私たちが違う時代から来たが、共通点があると思う。"

# game/room.rpy:650
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_e555018e:

    # n1 "Yes, yes! We’re all dead nyaw! Naomi knows what she’s talking about!"
    n1 "そうそう！私たちみんな死んでいるにゃ！ナオミが知ってるよ！"

# game/room.rpy:652
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_a2c7abae:

    # ee "A cute girl, dressed in a maid outfit, joins the conversation. Where was she hiding? Weird… By the way, she holds a plushie in one hand."
    ee "メイド服を着ているかわいい女子が現れてきた。今までどこにいたんだろう？変だな…　手でぬいぐるみを持っている。"

# game/room.rpy:654
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_50d5f946:

    # n1 "What, can’t you see it? You can, can’t you? You just don’t want to admit it… Ease up – death is the best answer-nya!"
    n1 "そうだろう！わからないの？まあな、確かに、それは受け入れにくいかもしれない。死だ。死が一番適切な答えにゃろう。"

# game/room.rpy:657
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_0082ea6d:

    # m1 "This little brat… She keeps spouting nonsense."
    m1 "どいつもこいつもばかばかしいこと言ってる。"

# game/room.rpy:660
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_36548f26:

    # n1 "Why, I’m just trying to play this game! Unlike you, I realized these are all answers and death is the best one of them all!"
    n1 "ただゲームのルールに合わせただけだよ！あなたと違って、これは全部答えだとわかった。そして、死が答えだとわかった。"

# game/room.rpy:663
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_8d206a1b:

    # ee "Ring-ring…"
    ee "ジャンジャン…"

# game/room.rpy:665
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_d5ff5190:

    # m1 "Death is certainly not an answer to anything, but, you know, if it helps us to get out of this place, I’m fine with it. I really need to head back home."
    m1 "死が答えだと言いたくないが、もしこの答でここから出られるのなら、いい。もう帰らないと。"

# game/room.rpy:668
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_f8d8e8e8:

    # n1 "No one likes the dead coming back, I’m afraid~"
    n1 "死んだ人が帰ってくると誰も喜んでくれないだろう。怖いわ～"

# game/room.rpy:671
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_10edb993:

    # m1 "I’m not dead!"
    m1 "私は死んでない！"

# game/room.rpy:674
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_a924797c:

    # s1 "I agree with Naomi… maybe death is the ultimate answer to everything. At the very least, it has the ultimate degree of certainty."
    s1 "ナオミと賛成する…　死は答えかもしれない。そもそも死というものが確実性がある。"

# game/room.rpy:677
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_6be526f0:

    # m1 "What?"
    m1 "どういう意味？"

# game/room.rpy:680
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_5da7b0a8:

    # s1 "Well, how do you know whether or not you actually live? What qualifies you as a living person?"
    s1 "生きているかどうか確実にわかる方法がある？生きている象徴は？"

# game/room.rpy:683
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_2cf8bddc:

    # m1 "Ridiculous. Don’t be silly. My heartbeat, for instance."
    m1 "そんなバカな…　まあ、心臓の鼓動とか？"

# game/room.rpy:686
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_20ce8586:

    # s1 "Then you compare yourself to an animal."
    s1 "動物も心臓が鼓動する。"

# game/room.rpy:689
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_00094163:

    # m1 "You’re getting on my nerves."
    m1 "むかつく！"

# game/room.rpy:692
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_5c42052a:

    # s1 "Hey, I’m just trying to say that, compared to the lives of some people, you’re just occupying space. On the other hand, when you die, you’re one hundred percent dead. Everyone is equal 6 feet underground. No one can challenge this fact."
    s1 "言いたいのは、ある人が生きるのではなく、生存するだけ。一方で、死んだら確実に死んでいるとわかっている。死んだらみんな同じく価値のないものになっている。"

# game/room.rpy:695
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_5bfadf91:

    # m1 "Spoken like a true genius."
    m1 "頭いいね、すばらしい。"

# game/room.rpy:698
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_4fa02821:

    # s1 "I know, right? I’m an underappreciated asset."
    s1 "だろう？人が普通気づいてくれないの。"

# game/room.rpy:701
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_46461007:

    # m1 "Where are you from, again?"
    m1 "どこから来たっけ？"

# game/room.rpy:704
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_84a541f5:

    # s1 "The present time."
    s1 "あなたは未来から来たのなら、私は現在から来ただろう。"

# game/room.rpy:707
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_3c658ae3:

    # n1 "Death is the answer simply because eternal life is much worse."
    n1 "死はいい答えである理由は確かに、もう一つある。不死よりずっといいから。"

# game/room.rpy:709
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_d077672c:

    # e1 "Say what?"
    e1 "何？"

# game/room.rpy:711
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_2e89f4f4:

    # n1 "I think I still have my magic powers to show you. Kitty cat, kitty cat! Make me happy, make them sad!"
    n1 "まだ魔法力があるだろうし、見せてあげる。猫ね、猫ね、私を幸せにして、彼らを悲しませて。"

# game/room.rpy:713
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_d49564e5:

    # ee "I’m quite sure she’s referring to that plushie."
    ee "ぬいぐるみと話しているのかな。"

# game/room.rpy:715
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_70808d71:

    # e1 "Um, so what’s going to happen now?"
    e1 "で？"

# game/room.rpy:717
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_9dacbfe4:

    # n1 "Eternity!"
    n1 "永遠！"

# game/room.rpy:719
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_1339ec42:

    # e1 "What do you mean?"
    e1 "どういう意味？"

# game/room.rpy:721
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_136d5ffa:

    # n1 "Time will go, but we won’t follow!"
    n1 "時代が変わっても、私たちはずっとこのまま！"

# game/room.rpy:723
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_91e9c136:

    # ee "And she was right."
    ee "本当にその通りだった。"

# game/room.rpy:822
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_1db227a2:

    # s1 "What day is it today?"
    s1 "今日何曜日だったっけ？"

# game/room.rpy:825
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_60e4a148:

    # n1 "Friday-nya!"
    n1 "金曜日だにゃ！"

# game/room.rpy:828
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_9e96918a:

    # m1 "Jeez, how would you know? Thanks for your trick, time lost its meaning."
    m1 "なんで知ってる？あなたのせいで時間の流れに迷ってしまった。"

# game/room.rpy:831
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_976d7936:

    # n1 "Therefore, it might as well always be Friday?"
    n1 "そうなら金曜日でも何曜日でもいいだろう？"

# game/room.rpy:834
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_d1fc1a68:

    # m1 "It’s been what… days, months, years?"
    m1 "もう何日経ったのだろう…　何年経ったのだろう？"

# game/room.rpy:837
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_391c93e5:

    # s1 "Hey Naomi, can you revert your spell?"
    s1 "ナオミ、あの呪文を切り戻しできる？"

# game/room.rpy:840
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_b80c981a:

    # n1 "Tee-hee… if you all admit death is the answer, maybe I could!"
    n1 "死が答えだと納得してくれたら、もしかしてできるかもしれない！"

# game/room.rpy:843
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_b8404223:

    # s1 "Okay, I admit it."
    s1 "じゃ、私は納得した。もういい。"

# game/room.rpy:846
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_e55242c7:

    # m1 "No way I’m going to fall for this trick. You want to stay here forever? Fine, let’s talk. Little by little, the future will come, and that’s exactly where I’m from."
    m1 "私絶対あきらめない。ここに永遠にいるつもり？なら、未来がきて、私の時代になる。"

# game/room.rpy:849
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_8cdca407:

    # n1 "Okay! Let’s talk about cats."
    n1 "じゃ、猫の話をしよう！"

# game/room.rpy:850
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_ca9491f8:

    # ee "So we did."
    ee "そして、その話をした。"

# game/room.rpy:856
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_da68c765:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about food."
    n1 "食事の話をしよう！"

# game/room.rpy:862
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_87a14ef5:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about fun."
    n1 "楽しいことについて話そう！"

# game/room.rpy:868
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_9cbe8c04:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about films."
    n1 "映画の話をしよう！"

# game/room.rpy:874
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_5a8cc362:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about fiction."
    n1 "ファンシーの話をしよう！"

# game/room.rpy:880
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_b7d8ac00:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about friends."
    n1 "友達の話をしよう！"

# game/room.rpy:886
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_16f0aa98:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about freedom."
    n1 "自由の話をしよう！"

# game/room.rpy:892
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_48c514a9:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about feelings."
    n1 "感情の話をしよう！"

# game/room.rpy:898
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_15420724:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about foals."
    n1 "子馬の話をしよう！"

# game/room.rpy:904
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_15658208:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about foxes."
    n1 "狐の話をしよう！"

# game/room.rpy:910
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_8805db41:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about forests."
    n1 "森の話をしよう！"

# game/room.rpy:916
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_39de2463:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about fonts."
    n1 "書道の話をしよう！"

# game/room.rpy:923
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_d5add85d:

    # m1 "Stop it! I can’t take it anymore!"
    m1 "もうやめてくれ！もう限界だ！"

# game/room.rpy:925
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_0f435484:

    # m1 "Fine, maybe death is the answer. Whatever…"
    m1 "あきらめる。死が答えだと認めた。もういい。"

# game/room.rpy:927
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_8da00748:

    # ee "I too agreed with that. However, nothing happened."
    ee "俺も納得したが、何も変わらない。"

# game/room.rpy:928
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_a5497450:

    # e1 "Uh, what’s next? What should we do?"
    e1 "どうする？どうすればいいだろう？"

# game/room.rpy:930
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_3d74f157:

    # s1 "I think we should be more proactive, now that we all agree on our answer. See this purple liquid? It’s the last resort liquid, so to speak. Let me help you, friends…"
    s1 "行動に移るんだ。この注射器の液体だ。この注射器を使って、みんなを助けるから、ね？"

# game/room.rpy:931
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_7db20d8b:

    # ee "She moves so swiftly. It doesn’t even hurt… My vision starts to become blurry."
    ee "急に動き出す。痛くもない…　目が勝手に閉じてしまう。"

# game/room.rpy:934
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_bf2f7a0d:

    # ee "Ring-ring. The phone rings again, but this time I manage to answer it, somehow."
    ee "ジャンジャン。電話がまたなってくるが、今度は電話に出ることができた。"

# game/room.rpy:935
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_9ae1ae91:

    # ee "The guy on the other end of the line tells me that if I die, I’ll stay in this room forever. Uhm… why haven’t I thought about it before?"
    ee "もし死んでしまったら、この部屋に永遠にいるってあの人が言った。それはそうだろう。確かに。"

# game/room.rpy:936
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_2b6f9836:

    # ee "I’m afraid it’s too late now."
    ee "もう遅いだろう。"

# game/room.rpy:940
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_761e2296:

    # ee "\"Love\""
    ee "\"愛\""

# game/room.rpy:941
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_d2faa229:

    # e1 "Love? What is love?"
    e1 "愛ってなんだろう？"

# game/room.rpy:943
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_4d464fd2:

    # n1 "Baby don’t hurt me… oh, pardon me! Hi! What would your order be?"
    n1 "ご注文はお決まりですか？？"

# game/room.rpy:944
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_95474de9:

    # e1 "Naomi? You’re… alive?"
    e1 "ナオミ？生きているの？"

# game/room.rpy:946
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_59914448:

    # n1 "Yes, why? However, I woke up in this room today. You know, that milk tea I had yesterday… it tasted so weird. Anyway, although it’s not my tavern anymore , I certainly have a customer."
    n1 "生きてるよ？なんで？まあ、今この部屋に起きたときちょっとお腹が痛かったけど。昨日のミルクティーがやっぱり変なにおいしてたな…　これはもう私の居酒屋ではないが、ちゃんとお客様が来てくれたね。"

# game/room.rpy:947
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_84a1e791:

    # e1 "What can I order?"
    e1 "じゃ、何を注文してもいい？"

# game/room.rpy:949
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_e20e6c41:

    # n1 "Nothing, I’m afraid. We’re short on everything. But I can make you company! I’m a good maid, after all."
    n1 "残念ながら、何もないわ。全部売り切れてしまってさ…　まあ、でも、仲間になれるよ！私、メイドだし。"

# game/room.rpy:950
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_b1a80b2d:

    # e1 "Did you see this strange whiteboard?"
    e1 "あの白板見た？"

# game/room.rpy:952
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_c2949f2c:

    # n1 "Sure I did! What do you think the answer is-nya?"
    n1 "もちろん！答えは何だと思うにゃん？"

# game/room.rpy:953
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_5b3ee10e:

    # e1 "Love."
    e1 "愛だ"

# game/room.rpy:955
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_51562a0a:

    # n1 "How romantic of you! Sadly, I know nothing of it. I’m not allowed to get into an affair with a customer, even with one as handsome as you. However… let my magic do the work and say whether or not you’re right-nya! Kitty cat, kitty cat, make me happy, make them sad!"
    n1 "ロマンティックね！私は愛が詳しくないな…　残念だけど。お客様との恋愛関係が禁止されてるの。あなたのようなハンサムなお客様だとしてもだめ。んじゃ、魔法を使って、あなたが正しいかどうか調べてみよう。猫ね、猫ね、私を幸せにして、彼らを悲しませて。"

# game/room.rpy:956
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_0c7888ba:

    # ee "Two other girls appear right in front of my eyes."
    ee "他の二人の女性が現れてきた。"

# game/room.rpy:960
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_8551e79d:

    # n1 "Tell me, what is love?"
    n1 "愛とはなんだろう？"

# game/room.rpy:963
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_3ffa9ff9:

    # m1 "Love is reducible to the absurd act of chemicals. Therefore, there is no intrinsic value in this material universe."
    m1 "愛とは、化学反応である。そんなものは価値がないし存在もしない。"

# game/room.rpy:966
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_31306ef3:

    # s1 "Hypocrite that you are, for you trust the chemicals in your brain to tell you they are chemicals. All knowledge is ultimately based on that which we cannot prove. Will you fight? Or will you perish like a dog?"
    s1 "そんなこと言わせるのは脳の中の化学物質だよ。その化学物質はなにがわかる？存在すると存在しないものの区別はなんだろう？愛が存在していないのをどうやって証明する？"

# game/room.rpy:969
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_7a418a0b:

    # n1 "Sorry, they’re a bit broken. Let me fix it-nya!"
    n1 "あの二人がちょっと狂ったっぽいにゃ。"

# game/room.rpy:977
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_8551e79d_1:

    # n1 "Tell me, what is love?"
    n1 "愛とはなんだ？"

# game/room.rpy:978
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_701124c6:

    # ee "Silence was her answer."
    ee "無言だった。"

# game/room.rpy:980
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_ba59fce4:

    # n1 "Oh my, oh my, still no good. Well, let me try this little trick! In a second, they’re going to fall for you, Hermes!"
    n1 "なかなかうまくいかないね。じゃ、これやってみよう。ヘルメース、これで彼女たちがあなたに惚れてしまう。"

# game/room.rpy:982
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_2b75df09:

    # ee "She spanks me with her plushie."
    ee "そして、ぬいぐるみで俺をひっぱたく。"

# game/room.rpy:984
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_3f6c2965:

    # ee "I notice Sophie and Megan staring at me."
    ee "ソフィーとメガンが俺をじっと見てるのを気づく。"

# game/room.rpy:986
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_1a883a9b:

    # m1 "Um, Hermes?"
    m1 "ね、ヘルメース？"

# game/room.rpy:987
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_e728d812:

    # e1 "Yes?"
    e1 "なに？"

# game/room.rpy:989
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_da584911:

    # m1 "I… I love you."
    m1 "私…　あなたのことが…　好き。"

# game/room.rpy:990
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_190fa817:

    # e1 "Why?"
    e1 "どうして？"

# game/room.rpy:992
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_e0b9e159:

    # m1 "Should I have a reason?"
    m1 "理由なんて要る？"

# game/room.rpy:993
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_ca4c5a22:

    # e1 "No, but I’m curious."
    e1 "いや、ただ聞いてみた。"

# game/room.rpy:995
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_cd0d4e7a:

    # m1 "Just because you’re here."
    m1 "ヘルメースがここにいるから。"

# game/room.rpy:996
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_9a0c13f9:

    # e1 "I’ve been here before."
    e1 "前からここにいただろう。"

# game/room.rpy:998
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_d1545791:

    # m1 "Really? Well, people change, don’t they?"
    m1 "そう？まあ、人が変わるもんね。"

# game/room.rpy:1001
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_5188dce6:

    # s1 "He’s mine! He will be my darling. Only you and I forever more, Hermes."
    s1 "いやだ！ヘルメースは私のダーリンになる。いつまでも、ずっと一緒にいよう、ね？"

# game/room.rpy:1002
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_ce95f0e8:

    # e1 "Hey, we’re kind of stuck here together."
    e1 "どうせいつまでもこの部屋から出られないだろう。"

# game/room.rpy:1005
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_63d0fcdd:

    # n1 "But if you could leave… which one of them would you choose to go with you-nya?"
    n1 "まあ、でも、もし出ることができたら、誰と一緒に出るにゃん？"

# game/room.rpy:1009
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_5db9a200:

    # n1 "You’re being weird. I don’t recognize any of these names."
    n1 "あなた、ちょっと変。誰の名前、それ？"

# game/room.rpy:1012
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_5db9a200_1:

    # n1 "You’re being weird. I don’t recognize any of these names."
    n1 "あなた、ちょっと変。誰の名前、それ？"

# game/room.rpy:1015
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_5db9a200_2:

    # n1 "You’re being weird. I don’t recognize any of these names."
    n1 "あなた、ちょっと変。誰の名前、それ？"

# game/room.rpy:1018
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_b7057560:

    # m1 "It hurts me that you’d think of other girls during a moment like this."
    m1 "こんなときに他の女を思い出してずるいよ。"

# game/room.rpy:1021
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_94d97829:

    # s1 "Yeah, how could you? It’s so selfish… from another side, love is the most selfish feeling anyway."
    s1 "そう、そう。なんてわがままだ…　まあ、愛はわがままさ。"

# game/room.rpy:1023
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_2f5d78a1:

    # e1 "What?"
    e1 "なんで？"

# game/room.rpy:1025
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_d4d70ff8:

    # s1 "Selfish, of course, if it’s not eternal… and what is eternal love? Eternal love means you should stay together until the very end. Till death do us part!"
    s1 "永遠の恋ではないと、わがままだろう。死ぬまで一緒にいる恋だけがわがままではない。"

# game/room.rpy:1027
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_98b90bd4:

    # s1 "Now, I’m sure that after some time you’re definitely going to choose me over anyone else. The question is, how can I be sure that your feeling lasts forever?"
    s1 "いつかはきっと私を選んでくれる。でも、それは永遠な恋になるかどうかはわからない。"

# game/room.rpy:1030
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_114a833d:

    # m1 "What are you talking about? Stop babbling nonsense."
    m1 "バカなこと言うのをやめて。"

# game/room.rpy:1033
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_98e9d238:

    # s1 "Trust me, my words make perfect sense. Here, let my friend explain this to you."
    s1 "確実なこと言ってるよ。友達に説明してもらおうかな。"

# game/room.rpy:1038
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_454940ca:

    # ee "She does a few quick swings, and shortly after that we’re the only ones standing in the room."
    ee "彼女が近づいてくると、急に部屋に俺たち二人しかいない。"

# game/room.rpy:1039
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_75b83749:

    # e1 "W-what have you done? How could you?"
    e1 "今なにした？なんでそんなこと！"

# game/room.rpy:1041
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_011582e6:

    # s1 "Same as you, I’m just being selfish. All fair and square! Fair… you know what? Love is not the answer. Love is not fair."
    s1 "ヘルメースのように、わがままだけだよ。正々堂々…　でも、愛は正々堂々ではない。愛は答えになれない。"

# game/room.rpy:1043
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_d47ffec2:

    # ee "I feel cold sweat dripping down my back. Sophie’s clearly bonkers, and I need to calm her down somehow."
    ee "怖い…　ソフィーが完全に狂った。なんとかなだめないと。"

# game/room.rpy:1044
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_fecabd29:

    # e1 "Not fair? But why? I always thought love is one of the best feelings in the world."
    e1 "愛は正々堂々ではないって？どうして？愛より世界に素敵な感情がないと思ってた。"

# game/room.rpy:1046
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_f3bb75fb:

    # s1 "I never said it’s bad, I said it’s not fair. Love should be mutual, but it never works that way."
    s1 "素敵ではないとは言わないよ。愛は不公平だ。両想いではないかぎり、不公平だろう？"

# game/room.rpy:1048
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_61d98b07:

    # s1 "Remember, Hermes, between two people involved, one loves while the other allows himself or herself to be loved. How is this fair?"
    s1 "ヘルメース、カップルでいつも誰か一人の気持ちのほうが強い。一人は愛しているが、もう一人は愛されている。不公平だろう？"

# game/room.rpy:1050
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_a8cb72eb:

    # e1 "I don’t believe you."
    e1 "そんなわけないだろう。"

# game/room.rpy:1052
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_b3c2b8c9:

    # s1 "Oh, and love is also very selfish, remember? Even more selfish than you and me."
    s1 "そして、愛がわがままだろう？私とヘルメースよりわがままだ。"

# game/room.rpy:1054
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_dc7a5c78:

    # e1 "What about love you have for your parents?"
    e1 "そうなら、両親に対しての愛は？"

# game/room.rpy:1056
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_ed3c846a:

    # s1 "It all goes down the same street. Every time you buy them something, you feel like a good kid. In a way, you buy it for yourself, Hermes... Now, what I’m going to do is to have you all for myself."
    s1 "同じ。両親にプレゼントを買うとき、自分がいい息子だと思うだろう。自分のために買うかのように。ヘルメース、これであなたを私のものにする。"

# game/room.rpy:1057
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_9e436be0:

    # ee "Swing! The needle bites me like a snake. My legs start to tremble."
    ee "針に刺されて、足が震えてくる。"

# game/room.rpy:1059
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_476cf9b6:

    # s1 "It feels so… satisfying!"
    s1 "なんと気持ちいい！"

# game/room.rpy:1061
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_ae199ff2:

    # "Sophie’s face is the last thing to flash in my mind before darkness covers everything around me."
    "ソフィーの顔を見て、暗闇に落ちてしまう。"

# game/room.rpy:1069
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_5a644da7:

    # ee "I’m back from the dead, it seems. Even more, the usual crowd’s here, as if nothing happened at all. The phone starts ringing again."
    ee "また蘇ったみたい。いつもの連中がそろっている。何もなかったかのように…　また電話がなってくる。"

# game/room.rpy:1070
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_0973f330:

    # ee "I don’t think I can get rid of that pain in my head, so I badly need to concentrate on something else… maybe small talk can help."
    ee "ジャンジャンの音はもう耐えられなくて、女子たちとしゃべることにした。"

# game/room.rpy:1071
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_598cb488:

    # e1 "Hey, do you guys remember what just happened?"
    e1 "今何があったか覚えてる？"

# game/room.rpy:1073
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_3bad760e:

    # m1 "Um, nothing yet? We have to find the answer, and…"
    m1 "ん、何も？答えを探さないと…"

# game/room.rpy:1076
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_0bf62620:

    # n1 "And I’m sure the answer is one of these words-nya!"
    n1 "答えはこの中の言葉の一つだにゃ！"

# game/room.rpy:1078
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_2ec0ee81:

    # ee "You’re kidding me. Have they entirely forgotten about what happened before?"
    ee "信じられない…　全部忘れてるのか…"

# game/room.rpy:1080
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_fba2a399:

    # s1 "Hm… which word would it be?"
    s1 "どの言葉だと思う？"

# game/room.rpy:1083
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_630b973a:

    # n1 "Easy… Hate! Hate is the answer!"
    n1 "憎しみだろう！憎しみは答えだ！"

# game/room.rpy:1086
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_15b26fae:

    # s1 "Why do you think so?"
    s1 "どうして？"

# game/room.rpy:1089
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_9b3d3d1b:

    # n1 "Well, I hate you all, so this word is definitely a suitable answer for me. "
    n1 "まあ、あなたたちがみんな嫌いから、この言葉が適切だ。"

# game/room.rpy:1092
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_1adc9e55:

    # m1 "For you, yes, for me, no."
    m1 "あなたにとってはそうかもしれないが、私は違う。"

# game/room.rpy:1095
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_0aee5c79:

    # n1 "But why would I care about you-nya?"
    n1 "あなたのことどうでもいいにゃろう。"

# game/room.rpy:1098
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_17c8dc61:

    # s1 "I wonder what’s your reason for hating us that much."
    s1 "どうしてそんなに私たちのことが嫌いなの？"

# game/room.rpy:1101
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_32f53bf8:

    # n1 "It’s simple, you know-nya… I hate you because you leave me no hope."
    n1 "あなたのせいで絶望したから。"

# game/room.rpy:1104
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_e6d2010d:

    # s1 "Why, I wonder?"
    s1 "え、どうして？"

# game/room.rpy:1107
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_32411d59:

    # n1 "If you’re right and I came from the past, then I see my future in the two of you. What can I say? This future looks pathetic…"
    n1 "もしあなたが言ってることが正しいと、私が過去から来た。あなたたちが未来だったら、そんな未来が嫌だ。"

# game/room.rpy:1110
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_83e47828:

    # m1 "But you don’t know us at all."
    m1 "私たちのこと、全然わからないだろう。"

# game/room.rpy:1113
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_f8f12659:

    # n1 "Even five minutes is enough. I despise you."
    n1 "5分は十分だ。あなたたちを憎んで仕方がない。"

# game/room.rpy:1115
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_532099d4:

    # ee "Her annoyance doesn’t seem to be justified at the very slightest, but I’m not surprised, as it fits perfectly with the weird ambiance of that place."
    ee "ナオミの憎しみが全く客観的ではないが、この部屋には客観というものがそもそもない。"

# game/room.rpy:1117
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_b0648637:

    # s1 "I don’t think hate is the answer because it’s too easy to hate something."
    s1 "憎しみは答えにならないと思う。憎むことが単純すぎる。"

# game/room.rpy:1119
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_f877b003:

    # e1 "And who said the answer should be complicated?"
    e1 "答えは単純でもいいだろう？"

# game/room.rpy:1121
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_decd0964:

    # s1 "What do you hate, Hermes?"
    s1 "ヘルメースは何が嫌い？"

# game/room.rpy:1123
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_852a002a:

    # e1 "Other people."
    e1 "人。"

# game/room.rpy:1125
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_552b1ac7:

    # s1 "Including me?"
    s1 "私のことも？"

# game/room.rpy:1127
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_d3978f51:

    # e1 "We just met, but I’m sure I’m capable of developing a whole nanoangstrom of hate directed towards you."
    e1 "出会ったばかりだが、きっといつかちゃんと嫌いになれる、あなたのことが。"

# game/room.rpy:1129
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_d1423817:

    # s1 "Why?"
    s1 "どうして？"

# game/room.rpy:1132
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_b93fe669:

    # m1 "Yeah, why?"
    m1 "そう、なんで？"

# game/room.rpy:1134
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_d256d946:

    # e1 "Because you make me feel like I’m not supposed to be here."
    e1 "あなたたちは俺がここにいるべきではないと思わせるから。"

# game/room.rpy:1136
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_ae425021:

    # m1 "What would’ve changed had we not existed at all?"
    m1 "私たちが存在しなかったら、何が変わる？"

# game/room.rpy:1139
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_e6ce7e7b:

    # n1 "Then he couldn’t compare. If he had no other place to be, his thought would become invalid. I agree with you, Hermes. If I hadn’t seen the future right before my eyes, I’d have been fine with everything."
    n1 "私たちがいなかったら、自分と比べることができない。居場所がなかったら、その居場所がここではないだとわからないし。ヘルメース、私、あなたと賛成する。もし、未来を見なかったら、今の人生が大丈夫に見える。"

# game/room.rpy:1142
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_740098a8:

    # s1 "You guys don’t even know about the right reason to hate everyone around you. I mean… they exist. They smell, they take space, they’re loud and annoying."
    s1 "あなたたちは人を憎む理由がちゃんとわかってないね。人がさ…　存在している。人が匂う。うるさくてしつこくて…"

# game/room.rpy:1143
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_aff9eaa8:

    # s1 "That’s why I always stay in my lab, so I could have some personal space. But even there, when I visit the bathroom, I look in the mirror and realize I’m no different."
    s1 "だからいつまラボラトリーにいる。誰も見ないように。でも、お手洗いに行って、鏡を見たら、あの人たちと同じ私がいる…"

# game/room.rpy:1145
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_f6bf548f:

    # e1 "What about you, Megan?"
    e1 "メガンは？"

# game/room.rpy:1147
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_7fd3821b:

    # m1 "I don’t know. In the future, our personalities are removed as they serve little to no purpose. We don’t live, we function. I still have some emotions but hate is too strong, it’s off limits."
    m1 "わからない。未来の人は個性が要らないから、捨てられている。私たちは生きているのではなく、動いている。憎しみが強すぎる感情だから、禁止されている。"

# game/room.rpy:1212
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_550e2853:

    # n1 "Hermes! Hi-nya! Finally, it’s only me and you here!"
    n1 "ヘリメース！やっと二人になったにゃ！"

# game/room.rpy:1214
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_f887d2da:

    # e1 "Where has everyone else gone?"
    e1 "みんなはどこ？"

# game/room.rpy:1216
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_bfd62e5b:

    # n1 "What makes you think they’ve ever been here to begin with?"
    n1 "誰もいなかったよ。"

# game/room.rpy:1218
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_97e6d0a1:

    # n1 "Anyway… I’m here to support you-nya! Trust me, hate is not the answer! Life, yes, life is!"
    n1 "あなたを助けてあげるにゃ！憎しみは答えではないよ！生、生は答えだよ。"

# game/room.rpy:1220
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_432f24e4:

    # n1 "I want you to know that you’re supposed to be here with me. Stay with me forever, Hermes."
    n1 "あなたの居場所は私なの。いつまでも一緒にいようよ、ヘルメース。"

# game/room.rpy:1221
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_2c13b61e:

    # e1 "Why are you so sure about it?"
    e1 "そんなに自身ある？"

# game/room.rpy:1223
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_0f6fd17d:

    # n1 "Because I don’t think this place was supposed to exist in the first place. It feels made up. Therefore, you fit in perfectly. Think of it as a new life for both of us."
    n1 "この部屋が作られているだろう。作られているなら全部ヘルメースのためだろう？だから、ここはあなたの居場所だ。新しい人生の始まりかもしれない。"

# game/room.rpy:1224
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_fe6e732f:

    # e1 "Life… you think life is the answer?"
    e1 "生か…　生は答えなの？"

# game/room.rpy:1226
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_577273e1:

    # n1 "Yes, because I want to spend my life with you."
    n1 "そう。一生一緒にいたいから。"

# game/room.rpy:1227
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_57d2f7bf:

    # e1 "What… what are we going to do?"
    e1 "一生だと…　なにする？"

# game/room.rpy:1229
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_684cb5b8:

    # n1 "Everything but one thing… we’ll never walk alone. And… you know, I’m a maid. I can always serve you a cup of tea when you need it. Trust me, having a friend like this is what matters the most."
    n1 "なんでもいい。でも、いつも一緒に。そして…　私がメイドだから、いつでもお茶を入れてあげるさ。"

# game/room.rpy:1230
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_e8238865:

    # e1 "Thanks, Naomi… I-I don’t even know what to say."
    e1 "ナオミ…　ありがとう。何言えばいいかわからない。"

# game/room.rpy:1232
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_072f1189:

    # s1 "It’s because you actually want to spend your whole life with me instead, you know."
    s1 "何言えばいいかわからない理由は、本当は私と一生を過ごしたいから。"

# game/room.rpy:1233
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_8faeaea5:

    # e1 "Hey, where did Naomi go?"
    e1 "ナオミ？ナオミはどこ？"

# game/room.rpy:1235
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_791c8d49:

    # s1 "It doesn’t matter. It’s just you and I here now, Hermes. You and I."
    s1 "どうでもいいだろう。これから私たち二人っきり。"

# game/room.rpy:1236
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_14657251:

    # e1 "What are we going to do?"
    e1 "じゃ、なにする？"

# game/room.rpy:1238
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_5e6d7832:

    # s1 "We’re going to have some fun, you know. Admit it, that’s what you really want. Everything else is just a façade to mask your desire."
    s1 "楽しむだろう。それはあなたの本当の望みだ。隠れようとしていたが、私がわかった。"

# game/room.rpy:1239
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_a7246076:

    # e1 "T-that’s not true…"
    e1 "嘘…　嘘だ。"

# game/room.rpy:1241
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_0dba7c36:

    # s1 "Well, do you want my friend to ask you this question again? He’ll get an honest answer out of you."
    s1 "友達に聞かせてみようか？"

# game/room.rpy:1242
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_dd9803ce:

    # e1 "T-there’s no need for that…"
    e1 "いや、大丈夫…"

# game/room.rpy:1244
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_e31fba8a:

    # s1 "See? Now you’re being frank. Don’t worry, it’s okay. Think of yourself as a part of a hunter-gatherer world, it will make your life a whole lot easier. It’s just you, the things you own and the things you want to own."
    s1 "やっと正直になったね。大丈夫。私をものとして思って。この世は弱肉強食だ。"

# game/room.rpy:1245
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_f6c62981:

    # e1 "But I don’t want to think of you as a thing."
    e1 "ソフィーをものとして思いたくない。"

# game/room.rpy:1247
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_8c9c6948:

    # s1 "Well then, someone else would, my dear, and you’d be surprised about the choice I make."
    s1 "他に人が思ってくれる。そして、ヘルメースはきっと私の選択に驚く。"

# game/room.rpy:1248
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_cedbf49f:

    # e1 "Life is not as primitive as you portray it."
    e1 "人生はそんなに単純なものではない。"

# game/room.rpy:1250
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_35f42b63:

    # s1 "Life works the way you make it work, simple as that. I want my life to be primitive, so here I am. You know why you feel like you’re not supposed to be here? Because you don’t even know what kind of life you want to live."
    s1 "人生はあなたによる。私が単純な人生がほしい。あなたは居場所がないと思っている理由は、その人生がどんな人生であってほしいかわからないから。"

# game/room.rpy:1251
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_cb55d00a:

    # e1 "I… well…"
    e1 "そんな…"

# game/room.rpy:1253
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_6c2834b6:

    # s1 "Don’t worry, Hermes. Let me take care of it. Let me comfort you, my dear, so you could forget about everything else."
    s1 "落ち着いて、ヘルメース。私に手伝わせて。全部忘れるようにしてあげるから。"

# game/room.rpy:1255
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_5615a6d3:

    # m1 "No way!"
    m1 "いやだ！"

# game/room.rpy:1256
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_d4ed5509:

    # e1 "Hey, what just happened? Where did Sophie go?"
    e1 "待って、ソフィーは？"

# game/room.rpy:1258
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_f8af7a15:

    # m1 "I got rid of that succubus."
    m1 "あの悪魔を追い出した。"

# game/room.rpy:1260
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_5be7b092:

    # m1 "Hey, stay with me, Hermes. I’ve seen the future, and it’s not the best one, I admit… now we’ll have a second chance to make it great."
    m1 "ヘルメース、私と一緒にいてよ。未来はそんなに素敵なところではないかもしれないが、一緒に未来を変えられる。"

# game/room.rpy:1261
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_14657251_1:

    # e1 "What are we going to do?"
    e1 "どうやって？"

# game/room.rpy:1263
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_b5e504d0:

    # m1 "We’re going to believe in tomorrow. If you think you’re not supposed to be here, make tomorrow the place to be. Please… do it for me"
    m1 "明日を信じろう。今はここにいるべきではないと思っているのなら、明日はここにいるべきだと思うようにして。お願い！"

# game/room.rpy:1265
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_f9c9172a:

    # e1 "Will you love me?"
    e1 "俺を好きになってくれる？"

# game/room.rpy:1267
translate japanese ermy_game_d1_17a917c3:

    # m1 "I’ll love the you of tomorrow, I promise."
    m1 "明日のあなたを好きになる。約束する。"

# game/room.rpy:1289
translate japanese close_game_02a0c651:

    # "Okay, I had enough... I should think of a proper way to give feedback on this masterpiece."
    "もう十分だ。エルミにどうやって感想を伝えればいいだろう。"

# game/room.rpy:1293
translate japanese close_game_done_5cf9fa4c:

    # "I try to push the button, but nothing happens. Maybe I should try tomorrow."
    "ボタンを押そうとしているが、何も起こらない。明日やってみよう。"

# game/room.rpy:1301
translate japanese sweet_home_d2_3aae40ef:

    # "Man, I'm beat."
    "あぁ、疲れた！"

# game/room.rpy:1302
translate japanese sweet_home_d2_a73a474b:

    # "My mind still goes over what I heard on the way home."
    "まださっきの話で頭がいっぱい。"

# game/room.rpy:1303
translate japanese sweet_home_d2_128fa27b:

    # "Never judge the book by its cover, right?"
    "見た目で判断しちゃだめ、だっけ？"

# game/room.rpy:1305
translate japanese sweet_home_d2_eca482cd:

    # "Should I give Ermy's game another go?"
    "エルミのゲーム、も一回やってみようか？"

# game/room.rpy:1306
translate japanese sweet_home_d2_dc694895:

    # "But first, let me check on my sister."
    "でも、まずは妹が元気にしてるかな…"

# game/room.rpy:1308
translate japanese sweet_home_d2_553dedac:

    # imo "I can't believe you came empty-handed again."
    imo "また何も持ってこなかったの？"

# game/room.rpy:1309
translate japanese sweet_home_d2_340597f8:

    # imo1 "That girl from yesterday came again, saying she needs to check on your progress."
    imo1 "昨日のあの女子がまた来たよ。お兄ちゃんはどうって聞いてた。"

# game/room.rpy:1310
translate japanese sweet_home_d2_0a61f002:

    # imo "I replied that you can handle everything yourself."
    imo "お兄ちゃんは大丈夫って言ったけど…"

# game/room.rpy:1311
translate japanese sweet_home_d2_86347a80:

    # imo "By the way, what was in that document she gave you?"
    imo "あの巻物って一体なに？"

# game/room.rpy:1313
translate japanese sweet_home_d2_84ec55af:

    # "Honestly, I forgot about that strange, pixelated thing."
    "正直、あの巻物のことを忘れてた。"

# game/room.rpy:1316
translate japanese sweet_home_d2_100c76d5:

    # "Hm... Is it a bit different today? Just my imagination, probably."
    "今日は…　何かが違う？いや、そんなわけないだろう。"

# game/room.rpy:1319
translate japanese sweet_home_d2_7dc3beab:

    # "Same as yesterday... Who on earth writes this nonsense?"
    "昨日と同じ…　誰がこんなくだらないものを書いたのだろう？"

# game/room.rpy:1322
translate japanese sweet_home_d2_e34cee22:

    # "Alright, time for Ermy's masterpiece."
    "んじゃ、エルミの傑作の時間だ。"

# game/room.rpy:1344
translate japanese ermy_game_d2_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/room.rpy:1346
translate japanese ermy_game_d2_b0d17d0d:

    # ermy_game "I’m in this room again, the girls staring at me, awaiting eagerly what’s going to happen next."
    ermy_game "またあの部屋にいる。女子が私をじっと見ている、これからどうなるか待っているかのように。"

# game/room.rpy:1347
translate japanese ermy_game_d2_d7cdef92:

    # ermy_game "Well, truth is… Nothing’s going to happen."
    ermy_game "でも、実は…　もうどうにもならない。"

# game/room.rpy:1348
translate japanese ermy_game_d2_7e05c898:

    # ermy_game "No one’s going to play this joke of a game, so I could as well just write a develop diary here."
    ermy_game "このゲームをやるやつがこのようにいないだろうし、これを日記にしようっか。"

# game/room.rpy:1349
translate japanese ermy_game_d2_b45014df:

    # ermy_game "It’s time to be fair with myself. I lack imagination to write anything at all."
    ermy_game "本当は俺が想像力が足りないようだ。"

# game/room.rpy:1350
translate japanese ermy_game_d2_dd5652ba:

    # ermy_game "It’s… I mean, I wrote quite a lot, but it took me so much time… and, the truth is, it’s all worthless."
    ermy_game "こんなにたくさん書いたけどさ。実はすごく時間かかったが…　全部無駄だ。"

# game/room.rpy:1351
translate japanese ermy_game_d2_814b700c:

    # ermy_game "The characters don’t live. They’re made up. I’m made up myself. I don’t know what to write next, I really don’t know. My mind is totally empty, like a… jeez, I can’t even come up with a suitable description."
    ermy_game "キャラクターが生きていない。作られている。俺自身も作られている。何を書けばいいかわからない。頭が空っぽだ。"

# game/room.rpy:1352
translate japanese ermy_game_d2_2c8600a7:

    # ermy_game "The plot, you say? It’s non-existing. It’s a cliché of a cliché of a cliché… Just like me. And you know what? That’s what people want. They don’t want my originality, but I fail even at copying things in a proper way."
    ermy_game "内容？内容もない。全部もうあった話、全部決まり文句で、俺のように。俺自身も決まり文句。でも人は決まり文句しか求めない。俺の個性が要らないが、俺は決まり文句をパクるのもうまくできない存在だ。"

# game/room.rpy:1353
translate japanese ermy_game_d2_c75f475d:

    # nvl clear
    # ermy_game "What did I want to say with all this? Who’s going to read it? Man… I wanted this game to be exciting, but it’s so boring. The characters, I’ve seen them all countless times… a random bunch of characters thrown together in one room. My game is empty. I am empty."
    nvl clear
    ermy_game "このゲームで何言いたかったんだろう？誰がこれを読むのだろう？ちくしょう…　このゲームを面白いものにしたかったが、結局つまらない。キャラクターがつまらない。ゲームが空っぽだ。俺も空っぽだ。"

# game/room.rpy:1355
translate japanese ermy_game_d2_6963404d:

    # ermy_game "The real answer is that there’s none. It’s all pointless."
    ermy_game "本当の答えは、答えがないこと。全部無意味だ。"

# game/room.rpy:1356
translate japanese ermy_game_d2_97b96169:

    # ermy_game "I wanted to turn this game into a dating simulator or whatnot, but how can I write anything about a date if my current goal is to hold hands with a girl?"
    ermy_game "恋愛シムレーションゲームを作りたかったが、俺はデートについてなにも知らない。手も繋いだことない。"

# game/room.rpy:1357
translate japanese ermy_game_d2_76d85975:

    # ermy_game "How can I come up with a decent plot if nothing happens in my life? I know nothing about the past and the future, and my present time is… well, nothingness."
    ermy_game "人生がむなしければ、内容が作れないだろう。昔のことも未来のことも何もわからないし、現在も…　虚無。"

# game/room.rpy:1358
translate japanese ermy_game_d2_f2e65807:

    # ermy_game "Jeez, I wish someone would just put an end to my misery. Maybe it’d be a decent answer, after all."
    ermy_game "誰かにこれを全部終わらせてほしい。これが答えかもしれない。"

# game/room.rpy:1359
translate japanese ermy_game_d2_76948168:

    # ermy_game "Or… maybe someone would give my game a positive review? Alright, alright, a negative one is also fine, at least that means someone paid attention to my game."
    ermy_game "それとも誰かがこのゲームにいい評価をくれるかな？…　いや、ネガティブな評価でもいい。それは誰かがこれを読んでくれた象徴だからネガティブな意見でもいい。"

# game/room.rpy:1360
translate japanese ermy_game_d2_2a72650e:

    # ermy_game "Hello? Hello? Just don’t leave me alone. Please… don’t leave me alone. I can be a good friend, I swear. How come there are so many people in the world yet I’m alone? Does it mean I’m the worst? No… no way. My game will show’em all. I just need to come up with a decent answer… Yes. Please. Don’t leave me alone…"
    ermy_game "もしもし？もしもし？お願いだから、俺を一人にさせないで。きっといい友達になれる。なんで世界にそんなに人が多いのに、俺が一人ぼっちのまま？俺が価値のない人間だから誰も仲間になってくれない？いや、そんなはずがない。このゲームで見せてやるから、俺の価値を。答えだけ見つければ…"

# game/room.rpy:1361
translate japanese ermy_game_d2_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/room.rpy:1367
translate japanese ermy_game_d2_2d2263b0:

    # "Alright, I {i}really{/i} need to discuss it with Ermy..."
    "これは{i}必ず{/i}エルミに説明してもらわなきゃ…"

# game/room.rpy:1368
translate japanese ermy_game_d2_40cf4884:

    # "Let's hope it's just a joke."
    "冗談だといいな。"

# game/room.rpy:1369
translate japanese ermy_game_d2_040e97b3:

    # "Okay, time to do my homework."
    "じゃ、宿題しよう。"

# game/room.rpy:1378
translate japanese sweet_home_d3_4271d4ca:

    # "I don't feel too well. Better get to sleep early..."
    "ちょっと体調が悪くなってきた。今日早く寝ないと…"

# game/room.rpy:1379
translate japanese sweet_home_d3_c447ce57:

    # "I wonder what my sister's doing."
    "妹何してるんだろう。"

# game/room.rpy:1381
translate japanese sweet_home_d3_7714a930:

    # imo "Your face is all red!"
    imo "顔が真っ赤！"

# game/room.rpy:1382
translate japanese sweet_home_d3_2f86c619:

    # imo "Are you okay?"
    imo "大丈夫？"

# game/room.rpy:1383
translate japanese sweet_home_d3_7aa1715f:

    # imo "Tomorrow is Friday, will you spent time with me?"
    imo "明日金曜日だね、一緒に遊んでくれる？"

# game/room.rpy:1384
translate japanese sweet_home_d3_502bc282:

    # imo "By the way, that girl came yet again!"
    imo "ちなみにあの女子、また来たの！"

# game/room.rpy:1386
translate japanese sweet_home_d3_6aeb90bf:

    # "My head hurts."
    "頭痛はやばい…"

# game/room.rpy:1387
translate japanese sweet_home_d3_d5c5e305:

    # "That girl... Oh, right, the scroll..."
    "あの女子…　あ、巻物も…"

# game/room.rpy:1390
translate japanese sweet_home_d3_ea03ba1d:

    # "It's different again, but I'm too tired to be surprised about it."
    "また形が変わったか。疲れすぎて気にしないことにした。"

# game/room.rpy:1392
translate japanese sweet_home_d3_f36cae6d:

    # "Enough with it. I better go to bed... now..."
    "もういい。寝よう…　"

